description:
*Not sure the negative review with not being able to load a plan, if you are having issues please contact us support@engineequalscar.com. Some users have reported that they have to restart the tablet for the file to show in the load file picker, I will file this with HP.

Planning work for your team, managing multiple project, just need to have the resource allocations with you. Project Viewer is ideal for you. A must have for project managers, resource managers or group coordinators. 

This application allows you to export project plans from Project in xml so you can take them with you and have them at your finger tips. You can see Task name, start and finish dates, work, actual work, resource and the project GANTT chart. (If you would like other columns please let us know and we will add them for you.)


Project Viewer is Engine Equals Car's first in a series of application aimed at business users. Watch for more great applications aimed at business user soon.
